{"tid":1811272,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實除左學生 都有一班唔敢出聲既人需要支援","createTime":"2020-01-04T14:04:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-05T08:07:19.000Z","uid":218414,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f02b877cf94cefe535fc0bef1457f9278c158258","tid":1811272,"uid":218414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T14:04:51.000Z","msg":"利申 一名90後廢絲<br />\n佔中時有去過 但絕對唔係踴躍分子<br />\n2019年 我同好多港豬一樣 被一班小朋友喚醒左<br />\n第一次遊行係200萬01人<br />\n之後大大小小 人鏈 機場 罷工 我都有參與<br />\n<br />\n本人有工作 有個一歲既女<br />\n屋企人老公個邊全藍 <br />\n自己個老豆深藍 相親都退左休<br />\n立場 612 星火我都有捐<br />\n食飯即使工作地區得幾間黃店 都不停loop住食<br />\n<br />\n但係<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 對唔住各位手足<br />\n如果仲有機會 我一定會keep住呢個抗爭模式生活<br />\n<br />\n小朋友冇飯食 可以去黃店俾張學生證<br />\n可以tg搵家長<br />\n我12月開始搵左幾個同路人<br />\n甚至大J  都冇回覆過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係如果 我有一段時間見唔到個女<br />\n我想安心上路 手足 可以幫我照顧我個女嗎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/支援成年手足/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%E6%94%AF%E6%8F%B4%E6%88%90%E5%B9%B4%E6%89%8B%E8%B6%B3%2F&d=x%2FFuRRgY0RqQB1T9iHKuLS3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=ae0a13de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/支援成年手足/</a>"},{"pid":"fb8157e28f33c84bb4814bf26cc21c11638b9ce8","tid":1811272,"uid":74663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T14:33:13.000Z","msg":"幫你推 利申學生"},{"pid":"9268fa6fe03962905e743a854b02ea098ec88250","tid":1811272,"uid":103521,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T14:35:21.000Z","msg":"囡囡要人睇／教，可以幫"},{"pid":"6908574d92a42f866d9032b9bb0f95846cccc28b","tid":1811272,"uid":108579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T14:42:49.000Z","msg":"學生一推"},{"pid":"258cc6399031016ad